                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The function returns a decimal number with a precision of 10 and a scale of 2. This indicates that the function outputs a numeric value with up to 10 digits, including 2 digits after the decimal point."
